align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">第十六条</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><SPAN 
style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">符合金融负债定义，但同时具有下列特征的可回售</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">工具，应当分类为权益工具：</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（一）赋予持有方在企业清算时按比例份额获得该企业净资产的</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">权利。这里所指企业净资产是扣除所有优先于该工具对企业资产要求</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">权之后的剩余资产；这里所指按比例份额是清算时将企业的净资产分</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">拆为金额相等的单位，并且将单位金额乘以持有方所持有的单位数量。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（二）该工具所属的类别次于其他所有工具类别，即该工具在归</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">属于该类别前无须转换为另一种工具，且在清算时对企业资产没有优</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">先于其他工具的要求权。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（三）该工具所属的类别中（该类别次于其他所有工具类别），</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">所有工具具有相同的特征（例如它们必须都具有可回售特征，并且用</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">于计算回购或赎回价格的公式或其他方法都相同）。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（四）除了发行方应当以现金或其他金融资产回购或赎回该工具</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">的合同义务外，该工具不满足本准则规定的金融负债定义中的任何其</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">他特征。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（五）该工具在存续期内的预计现金流量总额，应当实质上基于</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">该工具存续期内企业的损益、已确认净资产的变动、已确认和未确认</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">净资产的公允价值变动（不包括该工具的任何影响）。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">可回售工具，是指根据合同约定，持有方有权将该工具回售给发</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">行方以获取现金或其他金融资产的权利，或者在未来某一不确定事项</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">发生或者持有方死亡或退休时，自动回售给发行方的金融工具。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">第十七条</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">符合金融负债定义，但同时具有下列特征的发行方</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">仅在清算时才有义务向另一方按比例交付其净资产的金融工具，应当</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">分类为权益工具：</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（一）赋予持有方在企业清算时按比例份额获得该企业净资产的</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">权利；</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（二）该工具所属的类别次于其他所有工具类别；</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（三）该工具所属的类别中（该类别次于其他所有工具类别），</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">发行方对该类别中所有工具都应当在清算时承担按比例份额交付其</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
