style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（二）因继续涉入导致企业发生损失的最大风险敞口及确定方法。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（三）应当或可能回购已终止确认的金融资产需要支付的未折现</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">现金流量（如期权协议中的行权价格）或其他应向转入方支付的款项，</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">以及对这些现金流量或款项的到期期限分析。如果到期期限可能为一</SPAN><SPAN 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Arial",sans-serif; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'> 
</SPAN><SPAN 
